Uziel Martínez, a teacher from Baja California, Mexico, has revealed how he donated his kidney to the mother of his girlfriend who left after a month and got married to another man. Martínez disclosed this in a series of videos posted on TikTok, expressing that he is still recovering from the kidney transplant. According to his statement on Mexico Daily News, he doesn’t any grudge against his ex-girlfriend despite her actions. How New APC Chairman Will Emerge Nothing Will Bring Me Back To Politics, Says  Obasanjo He said, “I don’t have anything against her. We’re not friends but we don’t hate each other. I only made the video for TikTok, I didn’t think it would get out of control”.